the creation of the official state radio broadcaster! When this was launched no one probably expected to still be here writing about it more than two decades on.

Radio Kiribati has undertaken enormous efforts not only during its creation but also through every year of its operation because without these sacrifices we would not have made it through the following years.

This is because we made wrong proposals a few years back and used them for the grant proposals to help radio Kiribati. These were later terminated and sent back to us, but that didn’t bring us to a stop.

If a proposal is not approved, it no longer means that your relationship with it has to burst into pieces. Rather it means start thinking otherwise about it and still move on with it.

Radio Kiribati went back and reinvented another proposal which was eventually approved and it’s now known as Radio Kiribati through the facilitating organization JICA.

radio has defeated all odds and it is now being so efficient not because of situation but because there is determination spirit, there is significant evidence making all these to happen.

One of the important things that made radio Kiribati achieved its target is because of the statement made by the previous executive officer of JICA Mr Sekigawa, when he said that radios feed the adolescents, its enhance their mental development.
